org.cytoscape.dyn.internal.model.attribute
Interface DynAttribute<T>

Type Parameters:
T -
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractDynAttribute, DynBooleanAttribute, DynDoubleAttribute, DynIntegerAttribute, DynPaintAttribute, DynShapeAttribute, DynStringAttribute
public interface DynAttribute<T>

DynAttribute is the interface to represents dynamic attributes, i.e. a list of intervals containing the value of type T and the time interval. The intervals list is not used to search for the current intervals, instead intervals are also stored into DynIntervalTrees, which provide much faster search time.

Author:
Sabina Sara Pfister
